<ul>
<li>Monthly membership fees are pre-billed and start at $59.99/month. Once you pay the membership fee, you will have access to Cortiam's services for 30 days. Customers can cancel service at any time*. If you decide to cancel your Cortiam Service, your subscription will remain active until the next billing cycle.</li>
