	</ul>
</li>
<li>The billing cycle will begin the day after the free trial period is over.</li>
<li>Monthly membership fees will be billed to the preferred payment method on file after the free trial period expires.</li>
<li>Services will be temporarily suspended when the trial period ends if there is no payment method on file.</li>
<li>You will continue to have access to all membership services up until the next billing cycle.</li>
<li>Leads start as low as $99. When a customer selects you as their real estate agent, you will have 72 hours to pay for the lead.
	<ul>
	<li>After 72 hours, We will return Qualified Leads to the Available Listings Pool.</li>
	<li>If a property owner changes their mind after you have paid for the lead, you will have five business days to send us a system message requesting a refund. We will review all requests for refunds within 48 hours. Cortiam reserves the right to refuse any refund that violates our refund policy.</li>
	<li>Leads will automatically be charged to the payment method on your account. We recommend updating your payment method before purchasing a lead if you want to use a different form of payment.</li>
	<li>Excessive patterns of winning leads and failing to complete the purchase within 72 hours will result in the cancellation of membership services.</li>
	</ul>
</li>
</ul>
